<h2 local-id=3D"991fa72a-2aef-43a1-8e37-074d56d6150b" id=3D"ApplicationArch=
itecture-TheFutureofReflow">The Future of Reflow</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"e294effe-ca7a-44e5-896a-a244ef230e42">
<li local-id=3D"2e742d90-cbe2-4d99-b758-96627d896217">
<p local-id=3D"ccc807f9-a59b-4921-b9ab-8a905e5b0863">Survey:<br>
=E2=80=94 How and where is Reflow used? What isn=E2=80=99t used? What is ba=
rely used?<br>
=E2=80=94 Who manages G3CBO? How? How often? To what purpose<br>
=E2=80=94 What are reflow=E2=80=99s strong suits (that if remade will requi=
re a considerable effort)?<br>
=E2=80=94 What are its weak points?</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e048798-df7c-4a94-9663-b2bdcecd2093">
<p local-id=3D"fd0c2ee2-d643-454e-b5a4-61f064e192ff">How can we reuse reflo=
