8?ref=3Dconfluence" target=3D"_blank" data-linked-resource-id=3D"4546101262=
" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://mcesys.atlassian.net/wiki">Eli Cohen</a>)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"a29989c4-5249-462b-8356-301616e56356">
<p local-id=3D"43040bcc-87ef-40f4-90d3-d6f3b5ff3663">How should &amp; can R=
eflow be remodeled? Where? For what purpose/project?</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"5098b7d7-1125-4f45-a08c-31cf096f3afe" id=3D"ApplicationArch=
itecture-ConfiguringMCEApplications">Configuring MCE Applications</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"28c6899d-8aaf-449d-8213-f0d83215699f">
<li local-id=3D"71a387d4-956f-4008-881f-a4680a749122">
<p local-id=3D"bb532bf9-b020-44ff-8686-897ceb873740">Survey:<br>
=E2=80=94 How and where, and by whom, the configuration is used?<br>
