<li local-id=3D"7719e8de-3b2b-46bf-acd0-12ec87b652f9">
<p local-id=3D"e672cfd4-9ee2-4e55-8ffe-9809d108bb1b">How do we deliver MCE =
products as an ecosystem for managing various client functions and services=
?</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce6c8862-679d-4782-914a-7b85ef2e41ea">
<p local-id=3D"97dad6bb-30c0-4c19-afa7-a22d9ad56b11">How does configuration=
 factor in?</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"242674fa-bbe4-4968-94e6-7f70e7c8aa6a">
<p local-id=3D"94d4b515-9561-46c5-a27f-d9b8415e1ad3">How do we put limits o=
n the configuration-based approach in order for us not to drown in the conf=
iguration-hell antipattern?</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8694346a-e0a8-462d-b657-1f8a739620ce">
<p local-id=3D"89231c9f-a159-4c9c-91f4-b9032e6efc86">What are the current G=
3CBO strong points that we want to conserve &amp; use in future?</p></li>
</ul>
